lead_paragraph: Mike Leake pitched four scoreless innings and Stephen Piscotty homered twice on Thursday, leading the St. Louis Cardinals to a 9-1 victory over a split squad of New York Yankees.

headline.print_headline: Leake, Piscotty Help Cardinals Beat Yankees 9-1
